@startuml UC6: Reservation Change - Create Request Normal

!theme plain

autonumber

actor User
participant "System" as System
participant "Server" as Server

== Create Change Request ==

User -> System: Press "Order Change Request" Button
System -> Server: Request Create Change Request
Server -> Server: Check Order Ownership
Server -> Server: Check Change Deadline\n(3 days before delivery)
Server -> Server: Check Pending Requests
Server -> Server: Calculate New Order Amount
Server -> Server: Validate Inventory
Server -> Server: Calculate Change Fee
Server -> Server: Calculate Price Difference
Server -> System: Change Request Created
System -> User: Display Change Request Accepted

@enduml
